$ IT Service Management
@ ITSM

The goal of ITSM is to implement and manage *quality IT services* that meet the needs of the business.

ITSM is concerned with activities such as
  • Design
  • Planning
  • Delivering
  • Operating
  • Controlling

ITSM is carried out by *IT service providers*.

{ Service desk #itsm-service-desk

  A primary function within ITSM is the ~service desk~ (see → development/IT/ITIL[ITIL]). The service desk provides a *single point of contact* (SPOC) for service users and
  service providers (the latter typically working in IT).

}
